# [pl] Na początku tury [gold]Zmień[/gold] [blue]{Amount}[/blue]
# {Amount:plural:kartę|karty|kart} w [gold]ręce[/gold].
# [ru] [gold]Преобразует[/gold] [blue]{Amount}[/blue]
